WEBVTT

0:00:03.680 --> 0:00:08.400
NARRATOR: For a time, the humans of Sera 
knew the illusion of peace

0:00:08.400 --> 0:00:13.400
[Building being destroyed]

0:00:10.800 --> 0:00:12.000
until

0:00:13.200 --> 0:00:14.800
[EXPLOTIONS]

0:00:14.800 --> 0:00:18.400
[CORPSER EMERGING AND GROWLING]

0:00:16.320 --> 0:00:18.000
emergence day

0:00:18.400 --> 0:00:20.400
[WRETCHES EMERGING]

0:00:21.200 --> 0:00:24.600
[STEPS AND SHOTS]

0:00:24.800 --> 0:00:27.800
[LANCER'S CHAINSAW]

0:00:25.200 --> 0:00:27.500
MARCUS: AHHHH!!

0:00:27.840 --> 0:00:31.000
NARRATOR: in time. Their valiant defense

0:00:32.340 --> 0:00:33.400
was crushed. 

0:00:35.300 --> 0:00:37.100
With billions dead 

0:00:38.640 --> 0:00:41.000
humans denied their enemy control

0:00:31.000 --> 0:00:33.000
[BRUMAK BREAKING A BUILDING AND GROULING]

0:00:36.500 --> 0:00:39.700
[SHOTS AND STEPS]

0:00:40.500 --> 0:00:45.700
[HEAVY LASER BEAMS]

0:00:46.800 --> 0:00:51.400
[ENOURMOUS EXPLOTION]

0:00:45.120 --> 0:00:48.260
by destroying their own civilization.

0:00:52.200 --> 0:01:05.700
[SHOTS]

0:00:53.200 --> 0:00:54.400
MARCUS: UAHHHH!!

0:00:54.500 --> 0:00:55.500
Now 

0:01:03.400 --> 0:01:05.000
[BRUMAKS GROWLING]

0:00:55.500 --> 0:01:04.000
the long struggle against overwhelming 
odds approaches a final desperate stand.

0:01:06.100 --> 0:01:07.000
[EXPLOTION]

0:01:07.000 --> 0:01:11.000
[♪]